********************************************************************************
* Add Two Numbers
* https://leetcode.com/problems/add-two-numbers/
********************************************************************************

**
* Solution
**

    * Description 
        Iterate over both linked lists node by node and write the sum of their
        values to a new linked list. Limit each output node to a single digit by
        carrying remainders over to the next node. Nothing fancy here. The naive
        solution is the best solution. 
    
    * Time Complexity
        O(n + m)
        We iterate over both input lists once, and write a length O(max(n, m))
        output list once.

    * Memory Complexity
        O(max(n, m))
        The output list is at most 1 node longer than the longer input list.

